      "rarity": "uncommon",
      "type": "wondrous item",
      "desc": "This glowing-rune seed can be commanded (action) to sprout vines covering a held weapon or object, giving it a comfortable grip, automatic sheathing, and making it function as my spellcasting focus. I cannot be disarmed of the vine-covered object unless Incapacitated. A second command word (bonus action) lashes the vines at a Medium or smaller creature within 5 feet — on a failed DC 13 Dexterity save, it is Grappled and Restrained for 1 minute; it can use an action to attempt DC 13 Str or Dex to escape. The effect ends if I move more than 5 feet away. Once the vine lash is used, it can't be used again until the next dawn.",
